    <name>Grossglockner (Austria)</name>
    <desc>Austria | 23.5 km | +1640 m | 7.0% avg. Austria's grand alpine toll road from Bruck, sweeping past glaciers to the Hochtor tunnel. Approximate geometry anchored at the real trailhead for indoor training, not the exact road.</desc>
